1. *Mrak* se spušta nad grad. (Darkness is falling over the city.)
2. Ona se plaši *mraka*. (She is afraid of the dark.)
3. Želim da zavese budu debele, da ne propuštaju *mrak*. (I want the curtains to be thick, to not let the darkness through.)
4. Čekali smo u *mraku* satima. (We waited in the darkness for hours.)
5. *Mrak* je bio tako gust da se nije moglo videti ništa. (The darkness was so thick that nothing could be seen.)
6. Nije pametno voziti kada je *mrak*. (It's not smart to drive when it's dark.)
7. Čuo sam nešto u *mraku*. (I heard something in the dark.)
8. *Mrak* je opasan za decu koja žele da se igraju napolju. (Darkness is dangerous for children who want to play outside.)
9. U sobi je bilo previše *mraka*, pa sam uključio lampu. (There was too much darkness in the room, so I turned on the lamp.)
10. *Mrak* je pokrio grad kad smo se vratili kući. (Darkness covered the city when we got home.)